{"tid":1919873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人排隊世界第一，康文圖書館編","createTime":"2020-03-11T05:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T06:16:06.000Z","uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"01f54291dc694bf421dde3a6bd8904b6e590b5de","tid":1919873,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"康樂及文化事務署早前宣布，部分室內康樂場地及文化設施今日重開，包括香港中央圖書館及六間主要圖書館。而為減少人流聚集，圖書館改為派發籌號按時段入場，沙田公共圖書館於開館前半小時派發籌號￼￼，近 50 人在門外等候。職員向記者表示，現正派發的籌號為下午一點至下午兩點，籌號數目有 180 個￼。其他時段派發籌號的數目，將按當時人流而定。￼<br />\n<br />\n近下午 1 時，已獲籌號的市民排隊等候入場￼，人龍近百。圖書館入口有職員為進場市民量度體溫。￼<br />\n<br />\n香港中央圖書館及六間主要圖書館，即大會堂公共圖書館、九龍公共圖書館、荃灣公共圖書館、沙田公共圖書館、屯門公共圖書館和屏山天水圍公共圖書館的成人、青少年及兒童圖書館將於三月十一日局部開放，並實施特別開放時間（星期一至六由下午一時至八時開放，星期日及公眾假期由上午九時至下午五時開放）。為免人多聚集，圖書館將控制入場人數，於服務時間內分段開放，每節約一小時，並派籌讓市民以先到先得方式進館。十二歲以下兒童必須在成人陪同下才可進館。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/89186046_2917285071690427_6925215120725377024_o.png?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQmlh6kI9QjFs2ErhKwHgpPFQWSix0SbojI29xQuqgVk7QLtY0n46CRnlHodSe02DNU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=dd3e19ab6e86b05ea5e0034bb72607cc&amp;oe=5EA73542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F89186046_2917285071690427_6925215120725377024_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQmlh6kI9QjFs2ErhKwHgpPFQWSix0SbojI29xQuqgVk7QLtY0n46CRnlHodSe02DNU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Ddd3e19ab6e86b05ea5e0034bb72607cc%26oe%3D5EA73542&h=e052205d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/89561623_2917285195023748_6166345148855746560_o.png?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQmSZAp-POuX5J-kho97hlMYZ2QcoT4nu2kXQTiNCd4A32Q22AHPURRSankTE_FPZsE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=5e5f5b396791adadb7f73b515b226d13&amp;oe=5E903196\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F89561623_2917285195023748_6166345148855746560_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQmSZAp-POuX5J-kho97hlMYZ2QcoT4nu2kXQTiNCd4A32Q22AHPURRSankTE_FPZsE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D5e5f5b396791adadb7f73b515b226d13%26oe%3D5E903196&h=d6838f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/89702329_2917285121690422_4727526444656230400_o.png?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQl7uxv2ISGy0BzOm596XYD_Jd79TKieLFvgWaC72M_6cbWDPSy2H50n1tZZ2VRuvno&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=82ebde57f36fd1669c707f2eec29524a&amp;oe=5E90B46C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F89702329_2917285121690422_4727526444656230400_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQl7uxv2ISGy0BzOm596XYD_Jd79TKieLFvgWaC72M_6cbWDPSy2H50n1tZZ2VRuvno%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D82ebde57f36fd1669c707f2eec29524a%26oe%3D5E90B46C&h=abdf3e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/89036149_2917285088357092_7305305505784659968_o.png?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQnlaJYqRiDy1glbVdVULEMC7nBnc-ryQdYmixaMJ0cfKPRQJHyD47G3edSEEKjq7rk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=7e1b8f4def7d0306a0d4f611f702bb4d&amp;oe=5E968DBF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F89036149_2917285088357092_7305305505784659968_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQnlaJYqRiDy1glbVdVULEMC7nBnc-ryQdYmixaMJ0cfKPRQJHyD47G3edSEEKjq7rk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D7e1b8f4def7d0306a0d4f611f702bb4d%26oe%3D5E968DBF&h=ab666ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/87710447_2917285181690416_1751527340216680448_o.png?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQmm94RGzSATqtORZmMQLYZOMV8AGPIwp7uBjgdthL5UKABKr95kzcs-i0Ye35QFihw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=f9c215bbea1bbf3a7c80b62a8171ba1b&amp;oe=5E92921E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F87710447_2917285181690416_1751527340216680448_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQmm94RGzSATqtORZmMQLYZOMV8AGPIwp7uBjgdthL5UKABKr95kzcs-i0Ye35QFihw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Df9c215bbea1bbf3a7c80b62a8171ba1b%26oe%3D5E92921E&h=19b91316&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba330fd86a0bb1cd32e5bb9b8bc3372a4cfc0114","tid":1919873,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2c01deb8754e857ee1f0a5c95a3473ce6601dc","tid":1919873,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}